snippet.title: Every Indian During Holi | Ft. Tena Jaiin | The Paayal Jain
snippet.description:
Hey Guys , 
This Holi Video has every Holi situation we experience. How Indians celebrate holi . The crazy masti of Holi . Revenge wali holi , pyaar wali holi , dosto ke sath , holi fest ki holi , college wali holi , holi pool party , exams wali holi . During board exams skipping holi festival and studying whole day , Indian mom scoulding and letting go out tom play holi with friends on streets with water ballons , pichkari , herbal colors and forcing to go to tuition on Holi , deciding holi songs playlist , grooving on ap dhillon songs , enjoying bhang thandai , beer , gol gappe , dahi bhalle , gujia sweets , getting gifts from relatives gulal , rang , all the colors , pichkari , desi ghee gujia , hugging enemies sorting out the grudges , hitting with water balloons , water guns , dancing , enjoying holika dhayan , the festival of colors . Girls planning to go parlour after holi so that holi colours comes out with waxing , facial , eyebrow threading , while girl got her periods and is avoiding holi cause she can't deal with tampons , menstrual cups and pads . After marraige first holi , lakde wale in lakdi walo ke ghar , making dahi bhalle , dancing , colouring the newlyweds , new couple having their romantic holi in front of in laws , mother in law and father in law , devar , devrani , jethani , nanad all in Mom house . Planning to go out to celebrate holi with big group travelling in train bus to vrindavan , brij ki holi , jaipur , udaipur holi , mathura holi foreigners wali Holi . Society ki holi party with all the food stalls , rang , gujia , gol gappe , sweets , pickari , chandhan , bhang , kulfi . Ladies dressing like Hema malini , Rekha white suit , bandni duppata , doing holi fashion in indian traditional wear , buying Ready made gobar uple . Packing holi Gifts for Indian relatives , kids buying water guns every holi , asking more colours , discussing kodda holi of haryana . School friends deciding to play after school in school corridoor , Hiding colour packets in school bag to play holi with school friends , ruining school uniform with colours , mummy scoulding  . Chintu Chinki Bhai Behen after holi in stained holi colours Mom savitri feeding cold puri , thandi puri achar , sabzi , and tea , after bathing multiple times to get the color out , Indian family getting to bed to sleep , plans to eat faluda kulfiin the evening enjoying with a good movie . Brother going out with his bro friends again playing holi with grease . Sister telling Mom , and mom daughter freaking out  . Taking out revenge by applying colours, the foodies, getting painted first by the bf/gf, mixing pakka color into herbal colors, balloon horror created in society that we go through in holi days, and The Best Holi Fight between two groups.. Well you will love it and Relate with this video.. Enjoy and laugh out loud. 
Do Share it with everyone, Comment your fav part and like krdena Video guys.. Subscribe the Channel for more amazing videos . 
This video is filled with such memories and situations we all have been in. 
Relish and Relive your Childhood Memories.. You will have major nostalgia
Do share it with your friends and family  .. Comment down your Fav Part, 
Like, Share and  

Subscribe to our Channel - http://bit.ly/thepaayaljain | Press Bell Icon

Follow Us On Instagram

Tena Jaiin : https://www.instagram.com/tenajaiin/?...

snippet.title: Tere Bin Ep 19 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Nisa Hair Removal Cream- Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 19 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Nisa Hair Removal Cream - 1st March 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Nisa Hair Removal Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma

Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas

Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

snippet.title: Color Fest Season is Here! Clash of Clans Official
snippet.description:
Prepare for an overload of color - Color Fest Season is here! And for the first time ever - unlock the Painter Scenery with March Gold Pass! 



Follow us on our Socials!
Twitter ► https://twitter.com/ClashofClans/
Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/clashofclans 
Facebook ► https://www.facebook.com/ClashofClans 
TikTok ► https://www.tiktok.com/@clashofclans

Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. http://supr.cl/ThisArmy

From rage-­filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/

Privacy Policy:
https://supercell.com/en/privacy-policy/

Terms of Service:
https://supercell.com/en/terms-of-service/

https://supercell.com/en/parents/

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 20 Teaser - 1st March 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar
Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra
Mahmood Aslam as Malik Mukhtaar
Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

#terebin 
#yumnazaidi 
#wahajali

snippet.title: एक Haunted Bungalow के रहस्य को Investigate करने पहुँची Team CID | CID | Witness |सीआईडी|28 Feb 2023
snippet.description:
In a haunted house shadows of evil spirits are noticed by pedestrians. Sumer, Mugdha and Gini are attacked by an evil shadow. The next morning Mugdha gets to know that her brother Balvinder has got a job of a music teacher in the same haunted house. Since then Balvinder has gone missing and a blood-stained Tiffin box has reached his house. How will CID solve this case? Is the bungalow really haunted? Watch this episode to find out.

Show Name: CID 
Show Cast & Characters: 
• Shivaji Satam as ACP Pradyuman
• Dinesh Phadnis as Inspector Fredricks aka Freddy
• Ashutosh Gowariker as Sr. Inspector Virendra
• Dayanand Shetty as Sr. Inspector Daya
• Narendra Gupta as Dr. R. P. Salunkhe
• Aditya Srivastava as Sr. Inspector Abhijeet
• Shraddha Musale as Dr. Tarika
• Ansha Sayed as Sub-Inspector Purvi
Episode: 1344
Producer: Brijendra Pal Singh

#CID #livcrime #सीआईडी #NewCID #LatestCID

Click here to Subscribe to LIV Crime: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCzXpAx4v6rFLYXkJZ5nmSvQ?sub_confirmation=1

About CID:
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

Click here to watch all Witness episodes of CID:  
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL0y08jtgaKIWxYpzQWYlyxhEbdo9ElGhf

snippet.title: Watch: CM Conrad Sangma, sister Agatha Sangma in line to cast vote in Meghalaya Assembly Elections
snippet.description:
Meghalaya Assembly Elections 2023 is underway. Current CM Conrad Sangma and his sister Agatha Sangma were seen in line to cast vote in South Tura. Voting in Meghalaya for 59 out of the 60 assembly seats are under way. The northeastern state has recorded a voters turnout of 15.76% till 9 am. The polling will seal the fate of 369 candidates. Polling in Sohiong assembly constituency has been adjourned due to the death of one of the candidates. The ruling National People's Party will fight to retain power, while the BJP and Trinamool Congress will attempt to unseat the incumbent government from power.

snippet.title: Kiara Advani Wins Star Of The Year Award At News18 Showsha Reel Awards I Sid Surprises Her With Hug
snippet.description:
It was a big night for both husband and wife. While Sidharth Malhotra won the Best Actor (Popular Choice) award for his role in 'Shershaah', Kiara Advani took home the much coveted Star Of The Year award for her outstanding performances in films like 'Shershaah', 'Bhool Bhulaiyaa 2', 'Jug Jugg Jeeyo', and 'Govinda Naam Mera'. Kiara was over the moon for the recognition. As for us, we couldn't pry our eyes away from the newlyweds after Sid hopped onto the stage to congratulate his wife. Check out how the two packed on the PDA on stage. Watch the video to know more.

snippet.title: Bhool Bhulaiyaa 3 MOVIE ANNOUNCEMENT! | Kartik Aaryan | Anees Bazmee | Bhushan Kumar
snippet.description:
MASSIVE ANNOUNCEMENT! 
Bhushan Kumar, Anees Bazmee and Kartik Aaryan come together for Bhool Bhulaiyaa 3 Produced by T-Series 

The third installment of Bhool Bhulaiyaa will release in Diwali 2024!

After winning hearts of millions across the globe, the gates of ‘haveli’ will now open again for Bhool Bhulaiyaa 3! Following a massive success of Bhool Bhulaiyaa 2, producer Bhushan Kumar, director Anees Bazmee and actor Kartik Aaryan collaborate yet again to carry forward the legacy of the Bhool Bhulaiyaa franchise! Geared up to tickle your funny bones with some thrill, the makers give a sneak peek of this mega announcement by dropping a quirky teaser. 

Taking the fun and scare a notch higher, the trio makes a promising reunion with Bhool Bhulaiyaa 3! Starring Kartik Aaryan, directed by Anees Bazmee and produced by T-Series, this horror comedy is slated to release in Diwali 2024.


Produced by T-Series, ‘Bhool Bhulaiyaa 3’, directed by Anees Bazmee, starring Kartik Aaryan, this family entertainer is produced by Bhushan Kumar and Krishan Kumar will be releasing in cinemas in Diwali 2024!

snippet.title: राजपाल यादव, अक्षय कुमार और परेश रावल की डबल धमाल कॉमेडी | हस हस के लोटपोट करदेने वाली कॉमेडी
snippet.description:
Champak, a theatre owner, is in need of an actress and his employees, Bunty and Babla, help him in his search. They get into trouble after their bag is switched with another one containing drugs.

Movie - Bhagam Bhag
Starcast: Akshay Kumar, Govinda, Paresh Rawal, Lara Dutta, Rajpal Yadav, Jackie Shroff , Arbaaz Khan, Shakti Kapoor
Director - Priyadarshan
Producer - Sunil Shetty, Dhilin Mehta
Cinematography - Jeeva
Editor - Arun Kumar

एक थियेटर मालिक चंपक को एक अभिनेत्री की जरूरत है और उसके कर्मचारी, बंटी और बाबला, उसकी खोज में उसकी मदद करते हैं। जब उनका बैग दूसरे ड्रग्स वाले बैग से बदल जाता है तो वे मुश्किल में पड़ जाते हैं।

फिल्म-भागम भाग
स्टारकास्ट: अक्षय कुमार, गोविंदा, परेश रावल, लारा दत्ता, राजपाल यादव, जैकी श्रॉफ, अरबाज खान, शक्ति कपूर
निर्देशक - प्रियदर्शन
निर्माता - सुनील शेट्टी, ढिलिन मेहता
छायांकन - जीवा
संपादक - अरुण कुमार

snippet.title: Vilen - Kyun Dhunde (Official Trailer)
snippet.description:
We are thrilled to announce that we are soon releasing the full version of a musical masterpiece that encapsulates the very essence of life's beauty and complexity.

Kyun Dhunde is a journey through the ups and downs of life, a reminder that every moment is precious and should be cherished.
It celebrates the journey through different stages of life, showcasing the joy and struggles that come with each phase, from the innocence of childhood to the complexities of adulthood, you'll see a montage of people experiencing life in all its glory.

Khoya-250 gm 
Powder Sugar-1 cup

snippet.description:

Song: Aaha Hero
Movie: Ghar Banduk Biryani
Song Composed, Arranged & Produced by: AV Prafullachandra
Singer: Pravin Kuwar
Lyrics: Vaibhav Deshmukh
Choreographer: Ganesh Aacharya
Male Vocalists: Vivek Naik, Rahul Chitnis, Santosh Bote, Mangesh Shirke

Strokes: Tapas Roy 
Song Mixed by: AV Prafullachandra - AV’s Music Lab, Mumbai
Song Mastered by: Shadab Rayeen - Newedge Studio, Mumbai
Assistant to composer, Associate Mix Engineer: Vishal Sadaphule - AV’s Music Lab, Mumbai
Creative Executive: Sahil Kulkarni - AV’s Music Lab, Mumbai 
Operations Executive: Prasad Shrimant - AV’s Music Lab, Mumbai 
Recording Engineers: Dhananjay Sathe at TSM Studios, Rahul Sharma & Samir Dharap at Studio 504, Mumbai
Studio Boy: Akshay Kamble - AV’s Music Lab, Mumbai

Cast: Sayaji Shinde, Akash Thosar, Nagraj Popatrao Manjule, Sayli Patil
Produced by: Zee Studios and Nagraj Popatrao Manjule, Bhushan Popatrao Manjule
Creative Director: Nagraj Popatrao Manjule
Directed by: Hemant Awtade

Lyrics:
लाल लाल लाल लाल लाल लाल लाल
लाल लाल लाल आम्ही या भुईचं लाल   

कळली चाल चाल तुमची कळली चाल चाल 
करून आमाला नंगाड तुमी  झाले  मालामाल 
  
उठला जाळ जाळ हुभं पेटलं आभाळ 
आमी झालुया वसाड आता कळली बघा चाल 
   
दिलं काय, बोला दिलं काय 
बोला दिलं काय, बोला दिलं काय..?
दिलं काय दिलं, काय देलं
काय दिलं काय..?

छत दिलं का, नाय नाय 
पत दिली का, नाय नाय 
खत दिलं का, नाय नाय 

आहा हेरो...  

दिलं काय, बोला दिलं काय 
बोला दिलं काय, बोला दिलं काय..?
दिलं काय दिलं, काय देलं
काय दिलं काय..?

बाता मोठ्या करनी झीरो
काका केरो आहा हेरो 

आहाहाहा, आहा हेरो

भपका भपाऱ्या आहा हेरो 
लुटल्या तिजोऱ्या आहा हेरो 

लाल लला लाल लले
लाल लला लाल 
लाल लला लाल ललै 
लाल लाल लाल...

आहा हाहा हेरो
आहाहाहा हेरो

आहा ….. हेरो
आहा हेरो

दिलं काय, बोला दिलं काय 
बोला दिलं काय, बोला दिलं काय..?
दिलं काय दिलं, काय देलं
काय दिलं काय..?

दाम दिलं का, नाय दिलं
काम दिलं का, नाय नाय
साम दिलं का, दिलं नाय 

आहा हेरो...

दिलं काय, बोला दिलं काय 
बोला दिलं काय, बोला दिलं काय..?
दिलं काय दिलं, काय देलं
काय दिलं काय..?

कीर्ती रूंदी, मेंदू नॅरो 
काका केरो आहा हेरो

भेदाभेदीचा आहा हेरो 
तुमच्या गादीचा आहा हेरो 
वचपा घेयाचा आहा हेरो
हेरो हेरो हेरो हेरो...

योहोओ योहोओ योहोयेओ 

चालाचा आता नै 
तुमचा दंडुका 
हाताच्या झाल्या है 
झाल्या हो बंदुका 
लाला लालाला लाला लेरो

सोसाचं आता नै 
तुमच्या चाबुका
झाल्या है हाताच्या
झाल्या ओ बंदुका

होईला होईला पाह्य अता धमाका

आहा हेरो 

भपका भपाऱ्या आहा हेरो 
लुटल्या तिजोऱ्या आहा हेरो 
आहाहाहा, आहा हेरो

बारूदानी छाताडाच्या 
भरल्या बघा संदुका  
आता नै कै बोलू आम्ही
बोलतील ह्या बंदुका 
लाला लालाला लाला लेरो

चाळन झाली जिनगी सारी 
झालं सपान भुगासा 
इझून गेली आस जिवाची
इझला बघा दिलासा

भिडली गगनी 
तुमची पिपासा 

आहा आहाहा आहा हेरो... 

आमी या भुईचं लाल आमच्या रक्तामंदी जाळ 
हुभं पेटवू आभाळ आता कळली बघा चाल

snippet.title: Tapu Sena's Request - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3688 - Full Episode - 7 Feb 2023
snippet.description:
Episode 3688:Tapu Sena's Request
--------------------------------------------------------
Taarak and Bhide talk about the "Suvichar" when Babita arrives and Jetha gets swooned. Jetha tries to explain the true meaning but he rather complicates it. Bhide gets impressed by Madhavi's role as a businesswoman. Later, Gogi and Goli arrive at Sonu's house to meet with Bhide. They have come to request Bhide to get some new indoor games at the clubhouse. Bhide clearly refuses to buy any new games. Bhide tries to eavesdrop on Sonu, Gogi, and Goli's private conversation about some surprise gift. Stay tuned to find out! 

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Bhavya Gandhi
Episode No - 3688
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah#तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा#sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in """"Gokuldham Co-operative Society"""" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - Promoolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), a Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch all the episodes of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:  https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL6Rtnh6YJK7ZFhouqhrvP3Sx0U7qxdzJi

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3706 - 28 Feb 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3706: Jethalal Ki Pratigya
--------------------------------------------------------
Jethalal promises Babita the delivery of the famous Ramson 85-inch television. Iyer cuts their conversation and reminds Jethalal of their previous incident when they were unable to fulfill his boss' order on time. Jetha vows to shave his head if he fails to deliver the order before six in the evening. Taarak advises him to call Bagha and Nattu Kakka and inform them to keep the television as he has promised the piece to Babita. On the other hand, Nattu Kakka sells the same television to someone with a profit of more than one lakh rupees. Remain tuned!

Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: न टूटेंगे, न बिखरेंगे - बिना मावा हलवाई से कही बेहतर Gulab Jamun - एक-एक गुलाब जामुन स्पंजी और रसीला
snippet.description:
Masala Kitchen Me Aaj Ban Rahe Hain 𝐋𝐞𝐟𝐭𝐨𝐯𝐞𝐫 𝐑𝐨𝐭𝐢 𝐒𝐞 𝐆𝐮𝐥𝐚𝐛 𝐉𝐚𝐦𝐮𝐧 Recipe. Is Holi Special Style Gulab Jamun Recipe Ke Sath Festival Enjoy Keejiye.

#GulabJamun #HoliSpecialRecipe #GulabJamunByMasalaKitchen #SoojiGulabJamun #RotiGulabJamun 
--------------------------------------------------
👉𝐑𝐞𝐜𝐞𝐧𝐭 𝐔𝐩𝐥𝐨𝐚𝐝: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NS3O6RLrVho

Please Follow Me On:
👍𝐅𝐚𝐜𝐞𝐛𝐨𝐨𝐤: https://www.facebook.com/masalakitchenrecipe
📸𝐈𝐧𝐬𝐭𝐚𝐠𝐫𝐚𝐦: https://www.instagram.com/masalakitchenbypoonam/

Subscribe Karein Humare 2nd Youtube Channel ko: 
▶️𝐌𝐚𝐚 𝐘𝐞𝐡 𝐊𝐚𝐢𝐬𝐞 𝐊𝐚𝐫𝐮𝐧?: https://www.youtube.com/c/Maayehkaisekarun
--------------------------------------------------
✍🏻𝗜𝗡𝗚𝗥𝗘𝗗𝗜𝗘𝗡𝗧𝗦:
For Gulab Jamun
* Leftover Chapati(चपाती) - 2
* Wheat Flour(गेहूं का आटा) - 1 Tbsp
* Hot Milk(गरम दूध) - 1/2 Cup
* Milk Powder(मिल्क पाउडर) - 2 Small Bowl/90-100 Gram
* Baking Powder(बेकिंग पाउडर) -1 Tsp
* Ghee(घी) -2 Tbsp
* Milk(दूध) - 2-3 Tbsp
* Ghee(घी) -2 Tbsp
* Dry Fruits(सूखे मेवे) - 2 Tbsp
* Yellow Food Color(पीला भोजन रंग) - Some
* Oil/Ghee(तेल/घी) - For Frying

For Sugar Syrup
* Sugar - 2 Cup
* Water - 2 Cup
* Cardamom(इलायची) - 3
* Saffron(केसर) - Some
* Kewra Essence (केवड़ा एसेंस) - 2-3 Drops

✍🏻𝐑𝐄𝐂𝐈𝐏𝐄: 
For Sugar Syrup, keep the pan for heating & put Sugar, Water, Green Cardamom & Saffron. Cook till the Sugar gets melted & becomes sticky. 
For Filling, take some Raisins, Almonds, Almondette, Saffron, Cardamom Powder, Melon Seeds, Pistachio, and Yellow Tandoori Colour. Mix them well and make small balls of them.
Take leftover Chapati, roast them & break them into small pieces. Then put the Chapati pieces into the mixer jar, add some Wheat Flour & grind well. Sieve the mixture & add some Lukewarm Milk. Bind the soft dough, cover & keep the dough for 10 minutes. After then add some Milk Powder, Baking Powder & Ghee. Knead it first, then add some Milk if required & bind the dough. Divide the dough into two parts & make dough balls then press with your fingers and fill the filling in it and give a perfect shape. Fry them in Ghee/Refined Oil on medium flame. Put the Gulab Jamun in the lukewarm Sugar Syrup. Add some Kewra Essence & keep the Gulab Jamun for 1-2 hours. Garnish with finely chopped Dry Fruits & serve it. In this way, Halwai Style Roti Gulab Jamun/Kala Jamun/Mawa Bati will get ready at home
--------------------------------------------------

Thandai Recipe

Gujiya Recipe

Holi Special Recipes

snippet.title: Naveen Murder Case | Sensations Came into Light | Reveals Police | Hyderabad
snippet.description:
ప్రేమించిన యువతి కోసం తోటి స్నేహితుడినే హత్య చేశాడు ఓ కిరాతక మిత్రుడు.  గొంతు నులిమి చంపి.. కర్కశంగా తలను మొండెం నుంచి వేరు చేశాడు. ప్రేయసిని బెదిరించాడని గుండే చీల్చాడు. చేతి వేళ్లను నరికాడు. హత్య చేసిన 2 రోజుల తర్వాత మృతుడి తండ్రికి ఫోన్ చేసి ఏమీ తెలియనట్లు మాట్లాడాడు నిందితుడు. సైకోలా మారి హత్యకు పాల్పడిన తీరును చూసి.. పోలీసులే నివ్వెరపోయారు. హైదరాబాద్‌ శివారులోని అబ్దుల్లాపూర్ మెట్ పోలీస్‌స్టేషన్‌ పరిధిలోని నిర్మానుష ప్రాంతంలో ఈ హత్య చోటు చేసుకుంది.

ప్రేమించిన యువతి కోసం తోటి స్నేహితుడినే హత్య చేశాడు ఓ కిరాతక మిత్రుడు.  గొంతు నులిమి చంపి.. కర్కశంగా తలను మొండెం నుంచి వేరు చేశాడు. ప్రేయసిని బెదిరించాడని గుండే చీల్చాడు. చేతి వేళ్లను నరికాడు. హత్య చేసిన 2 రోజుల తర్వాత మృతుడి తండ్రికి ఫోన్ చేసి ఏమీ తెలియనట్లు మాట్లాడాడు నిందితుడు. సైకోలా మారి హత్యకు పాల్పడిన తీరును చూసి.. పోలీసులే నివ్వెరపోయారు. హైదరాబాద్‌ శివారులోని అబ్దుల్లాపూర్ మెట్ పోలీస్‌స్టేషన్‌ పరిధిలోని నిర్మానుష ప్రాంతంలో ఈ హత్య చోటు చేసుకుంది.

Farq Episode 36 - [Eng Sub] - Faysal Quraishi - Sehar Khan - Adeel Chaudhry - 28th February 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Farq is the story of two different individuals, Irsa (Sehar Khan) and Kamal (Faysal Quraishi) who come together to form an unusual union under compromising circumstances. 
From the outside, Irsa and Kamal seem not to be made for each other. They are too different in terms of character, life choices, desires and socio-economic background.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3703 - 24 Feb 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3703: Bhide Ka Sar Dard
--------------------------------------------------------
Bhide was overjoyed to learn of Tapu's girlfriend, and he made "sheera" to inform Madhavi of the news. By telling him the truth that Missa is only a friend and there was a misunderstanding, Sonu breaks his bubble. When Tapu arrives at the society's compound, he decides to play cricket with Tapu Sena in order to remember the memories of his youth. Jetha, Babita, and Dr. Hathi become the audience of the cricket match, Tapu plays a scoop shot on Goli's ball, causing it to strike Bhide on his balcony. Stay tuned!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3703, 24 Feb 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000211011

In a face-off between staying connected to your roots versus only advocating a modern materialistic way of life, who trumps? Bhagya Dile Tu Mala charts the story of the simple, rooted Bhairavi and a modern, materialistic Yashovardhan brought together by fate. Radhakrishn Raasleela- part 387 || Prem Ki Tulana ||  Radhakrishn | राधाकृष्ण #starbharat 
Radhakrishn Raasleela- part 387 || Prem Ki Tulana ||  Radhakrishn | राधाकृष्ण #starbharat

►*About*
-------------
RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!

snippet.title: House Warming ❤️ | Meghna Vincent
snippet.description:
Namaskaram,
                               Welcome to my house warming celebration! I am overjoyed to share this special moment with you all. This new home represents a fresh start and a new chapter in my life. I feel blessed to have this beautiful space to call my own and I'm so excited to share it with my loved ones.

Thank you all for your blessings and support. It means the world to me. I can't wait to create wonderful memories in this home and make it a place of warmth and love. Join me in celebrating this milestone and let's make it a day to remember!

If you enjoy my content and would like to see more, please consider subscribing to my channel. By doing so, you'll be the first to know when I upload new videos, including my upcoming house vlog series.

In these upcoming videos, I'll take you on a tour of my home and share with you some of my favorite decor ideas and organization tips. I'm excited to share this journey with you and hope
 that you'll find some inspiration along the way.

Once again, thank you for your support and I can't wait to see you in my next video!

Sithara Entertainments headed by Suryadevara Naga Vamsi will be co-producing this film along with Ms. Sai Soujanya (Fortune Four Cinemas). The film is Presented by Srikara Studios

Music :GV Prakash Kumar 
Singer & Lyrics - Poetu Dhanush

Dhanush, Samyuktha Menon,Sai Kumar,Tanikella Bharani,Samuthirakani,Thotapalli Madhu, Narra Srinivas, Pammi Sai, Hyper Aadhi, Shara, Aadukalam Naren, Ilavarasu,Motta Rajendran,Hareesh Peradi,Praveena

Shankarpali recipe or sweet diamond cuts are a festive snack. Shakarpara Recipe at home is a holi sweet. Shankarpali or Shakarpara is a sweet and crispy Maharashtrian snack

snippet.title: Vasundhara ने झुकाया Shraddha के आगे अपना सर  | Thapki Pyar Ki | Full Episode | Ep. 637
snippet.description:
Vasundhara ने झुकाया Shraddha के आगे अपना सर  | Thapki Pyar Ki | थपकी प्यार की | Full Episode | Ep. 637

Vasundhara manages to find a clue and trace Thapki. However Shraddha stops her from locating Thapki and asks her to bow down and beg for Thapki's release. Can Vasundhara rescue Thapki?

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. Over the course of the show, Thapki falls in love with Dhruv, but is duped into getting married to his brother, Bihaan. In spite of this cruel twist of fate, Thapki doesn't let her spirit fade and does all she can to be the ideal bahu. What does destiny hold for this charming girl with an unbeatable spirit?
